OL,3,CAverage energy bill to fall by #230
OL,4,Cfrom April, Ofgem announces
OL,6,FThe cost for an average household in
OL,7,FEngland, Scotland and Wales will fall
OL,8,Ffrom #1,928 to #1,690 from April 1
OL,10,FThe average household is to fall to
OL,11,Fits lowest point in two years from
OL,12,FApril after Ofgem lowered its price
OL,13,Fcap in response to wholesale prices.
OL,15,FThe regulator announced it is dropping
OL,16,Fits price cap by 12.3% from the
OL,17,Fcurrent #1,928 for a typical dual fuel
OL,18,Fhousehold in England, Scotland and
OL,19,FWales to #1,690, a drop of #238 over
OL,20,Fthe course of a year or around #20 a
OL,21,Fmonth.
