OL,6,FAlthough this is being pitched as good
OL,7,Fnews by energy officials - let's not
OL,8,Fforget that energy prices even at
OL,9,Fthese new levels beginning in April
OL,10,Fare higher than the start of 2022.
OL,12,FAnd we now have record energy debt
OL,13,Ffigures approaching #3 billion. So the
OL,14,Fplain fact is energy prices remain
OL,15,Funaffordable for millions.
