OL,4,Cfrom April, Ofgem announces
OL,6,FOfgem chief executive Jonathan
OL,7,FBrearley called the drop "good news"
OL,8,Fbut warned "there are still big issues
OL,9,Fthat we must tackle head-on to ensure
OL,10,Fwe build a system that's more
OL,11,Fresilient for the long term and fairer
OL,12,Fto customers."
OL,14,FHe said the regulator is looking to
OL,15,Faddress the risk of high levels of
OL,16,Fdebt in the system and said it will be
OL,17,Ftaking a step back to look at
OL,18,Faffordability across the market for
OL,19,Fstruggling customers.
