OL,4,Cfrom April, Ofgem announces
OL,6,FConsumer expert Martin Lewis gives his
OL,7,Fadvice on what the announcement from
OL,8,FOfgem means, and how people can make
OL,9,Fthe most of the cut in prices
OL,11,FMr Brearley added that in the long
OL,12,Fterm Ofgem "needs to think about what
OL,13,Fmore can be done for those who simply
OL,14,Fcannot afford to pay their energy
OL,15,Fbills even as prices fall.
OL,17,F"As we return to something closer to
OL,18,Fnormality we have an opportunity to
OL,19,Freset and reframe the energy market to
OL,20,Fmake sure it's ready to protect
OL,21,Fcustomers if prices rise again."
